-- ds.copy-regular:

A page is the root of the website. It contains layout, navigation, and other global elements and wraps around the content of the website.

-- lib.tip: If you want to create a page with documentation layout, use [doc-page](/docs/components/doc-page) instead. Which extends `page` and adds meaningful defaults to the properties.

-- end: lib.section

